it.polimi.ingsw.GC_32.Client.Game

Class ClientPlayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.GC_32.Client.Game.ClientPlayer

  • public class ClientPlayer
extends java.lang.Object
    this class is the client-side representation of the server-side concept of Player. Because client only show information on the screen, the information contained into this class (like all the classes of the client-side game model) is really less then the server-side equivalent class.
    • playerResources: resources of this player
    • cards: cards owned by the player (only the card name is memorized)
    • name: the name of this player
    • familyMembers: the family memebers owned by the player
    • bonusTile: string representation of bonus tile
    • track: the position of this player on the score tracks, each track contains the points quantity owned by the player
    See Also:
    ResourceSet, ClientFamilyMember, Track
